				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="dablink">This article is about the term as used in media and computing.  For other uses, see <a href="Black_and_white_(disambiguation)" title="Black and white (disambiguation)">Black and white (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
<table class="metadata plainlinks ambox ambox-content ambox-Unreferenced" style="">
