<div class="thumbinner" style="width:222px;"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Breadfruit.jpg" class="image"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/9e/Breadfruit.jpg/220px-Breadfruit.jpg" width="220" height="283" class="thumbimage" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/9e/Breadfruit.jpg/330px-Breadfruit.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/9e/Breadfruit.jpg/440px-Breadfruit.jpg 2x" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Breadfruit.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="http://bits.wikimedia.org/static-1.21wmf9/skins/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
