<tr>
<th scope="row" class="navbox-group" style=";;"><a href="Digital_photography" title="Digital photography">Digital photography</a></th>
<td style="text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;" class="navbox-list navbox-odd">
<div style="padding:0em 0.25em">
<ul>
<li><a href="Digital_camera" title="Digital camera">Digital camera</a> (<a href="Digital_single-lens_reflex_camera" title="Digital single-lens reflex camera">D-SLR</a></li>
<li><a href="Comparison_of_digital_single-lens_reflex_cameras" title="Comparison of digital single-lens reflex cameras" class="mw-redirect">Comparison of D-SLRs</a></li>
<li><a href="Sony_SLT_camera" title="Sony SLT camera">Sony SLT</a></li>
<li><a href="Mirrorless_interchangeable-lens_camera" title="Mirrorless interchangeable-lens camera">MILC</a></li>
<li><a href="Digital_camera_back" title="Digital camera back">Digital camera back</a>)</li>
<li><a href="Digiscoping" title="Digiscoping">Digiscoping</a></li>
